# MISSION: PHASE 02 - MEMORY OVERLAY
## Objective
Add compact visual indicators of past performance to the match list.

## Requirements
1. Modify `src/components/ResultsCalendarGrid.tsx`.
2. Add a "Win/Loss Bubble" next to team names if memory exists.
3. Ensure the bubble is compact (e.g., "2W-1L").
4. Add the same bubble to the `Live` division cards.

## Success Criteria
- Operator can see W/L stats without opening the match drawer.
- Zero performance impact on the 1s refresh rate.